1992;;Into the Sun;;American;;Fritz Kiersch;;Michael Paré, Anthony Michael Hall;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Into_the_Sun_(1992_film);;Paul Watkins (Michael Paré) is an American pilot stationed in the Middle East, who is taken off his normal duties to show an actor about being a pilot in US Air Force. Tom Slade (Anthony Michael Hall) is an actor who wants to "get the feeling" before he plays the part in a movie about fighter pilots. But when Watkins takes Slade for a ride in an F-16 fighter, they are shot down and find themselves in a real combat situation.